textAnnotations.description:
ALICES
ADVENTORES
IN
MICHIGANLAND
"Have you guessed the riddle yet of how my plan would actually
provide enough money to fix our roads?" the Mad Cotter said,
turning to Alice again.
"No, I give up," Alice replied: "what's the answer?"
"I haven't the slightest idea, said the Mad Cotter.
"Nor I, said the Meekof Hare.
Alice sighed wearily. "I think you might do something better with
the time than waste it in asking riddles that have no answers.
auchtoon.com
